 Dividing these two equations, we find: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tan(k_{\perp}h/2)=\frac{\kappa}{k_{\perp}}=\frac{\sqrt{k^{2}(1-f)-k_{\perp}^{2}f}}{k_{\perp}}.
\]

\end_inset

Similarly, for the 
\emph on
odd
\emph default
