\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\cot(k_{\perp}h/2)=-\frac{\sqrt{k^{2}(1-f)-k_{\perp}^{2}f}}{k_{\perp}}.
\]

\end_inset

 These are transcendental equations for 
\begin_inset Formula $k_{\perp}$
\end_inset

